sequenceDiagram
    participant Test as "Test method"
    participant Client as "SimpleGraphQLClient"
    participant Throttle as "GraphQLRequestThrottle (semaphore)"
    participant Http as "OkHttp"
    participant API as "GraphQL endpoint"
    participant Metrics as "GraphQLRequestMetrics"

    Test->>Client: executeQuery(query, jsonPath)

    Note over Client: Build JSON body, add auth header from EnvConfig AUTH_HEADER_NAME and AUTH_HEADER_VALUE

    Client->>Throttle: acquire()

    Note over Throttle: Semaphore, GRAPHQL_MAX_CONCURRENT default 16, 0 = disabled, waits up to 120 s

    Throttle->>Metrics: recordAcquireWait(waitNanos)
    Throttle-->>Client: permit granted

    Note over Client: Max attempts = 2 if idempotent query, 1 if mutation or subscription

    loop retry attempts
        Client->>Http: "newCall(request).execute()"
        Http->>API: POST query
        API-->>Http: HTTP response
        Http-->>Client: response

        alt "SocketTimeout or ConnectException, or HTTP 502/503/504 - retriable and idempotent"
            Client->>Metrics: recordRetry()
            Note over Client: Jittered backoff 250-750 ms then retry
        else success or non-retriable error
            Note over Client: Break loop
        end
    end

    Client->>Metrics: "recordCall(durationNanos, success)"

    Note over Metrics: Stack-walks to attribute the call to the test class

    Note over Client: Attach query, response and error to Allure if active

    Note over Client: Parse via JsonPath, errors at $.errors[0].message, data at requested path

    Client->>Throttle: release()
    Client-->>Test: "data String or TestResponse"
